=================================================================
Initial Setup
=================================================================
Put this in your .login:
setenv CVS_RSH ssh

Put this in your .ssh/config:

Host dosadi
Hostname solano.homeip.net
HostKeyAlias dosadi
User your-user-name-on-dosadi




Now check that you can login to the CVS server by running:

ssh dosadi

=================================================================
Initial checkout of CVS repository (only done once)
=================================================================
cvs -d username@dosadi:/home/mt/cvsroot checkout dns



=================================================================
CVS commands
=================================================================
1. Get the latest version.  Any changes other people have committed will
be merged into your current checkout.

% cvs update


2. Commit changes you've made back to the repository:

% cvs commit


3. Get information about one of your checked out file:

% cvs status filename




  





